# Enforce LF for all text files in this plugin so content hashing is identical
# on Windows and Linux — runtime/ carries the synced shared-runtime payload
# whose buildId (runtime-manifest.json) is a sha256 over the raw bytes of
# dist/assets/components/schemas; a Windows clone with core.autocrlf=true
# would otherwise get CRLF in the working tree and fail verify-runtime's
# buildId reproduction (and any byte-parity check against the main tree).
* text=auto eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.mjs text eol=lf
*.js text eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
*.css text eol=lf
*.html text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
